ts of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/108486/', '', 'Azelastine, Ketotifen, Promethazine', 'Methdilazine, Azatadine, Ketotifen, Alimemazine, Fexofenadine, Loratadine, Phenindamine, Desloratadine, Tripelennamine, Azelastine, Cyclizine, More', 1767369485);
